snippet.title: Turn Puzzles into Portraits with Pokémon Picross!
snippet.description:
http://bit.ly/1OJ5CY8
Pokémon Picross is now available to download from Nintendo eShop! Get ready to turn puzzles into portraits with Pokémon Picross! In this game, you’ll solve number puzzles to complete pictures of your favorite Pokémon and add them to your collection. Visit our site to learn more. 

Official site: http://www.pokemon.com
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/Pokemon
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/Pokemon
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/pokemon
